reg_info.act_under: Registry Act   Loi sur l’enregistrement des actes

content.content: 1. For the purposes of subsection 78 (10) of the Act, the Province of Ontario is designated as a certification area.  R.R.O. 1990, Reg. 993, s. 1.
content.raw_html: 1. For the purposes of subsection 78 (10) of the Act, the Province of Ontario is designated as a certification area.  R.R.O. 1990, Reg. 993, s. 1.

content.content: 2. Section 1 does not apply to those parts of the Province of Ontario to which the Land Titles Act applies.  R.R.O. 1990, Reg. 993, s. 2.
